The ultimate locations of these files are:

dhcpcd.conf[.aphost][.apclient] - /etc/dhcpcd.conf
rc.local[.aphost][.apclient] - /etc/rc.local
hostapd.conf - /etc/hostapd/hostapd.conf
default_hostapd - /etc/default/hostapd
dnsmasq.conf - /etc/dnsmasq.conf

*.aphost denotes files used when in configuration mode
*.apclient denotes files used when in regular use mode
